metadata.name: Sunny Day
metadata.description:
A fun ride on a sunny day around the countryside with some humming and birds chirping.


A little about the artist:
NBG is a 6 year old, self-taught animator. A second grader who has loved drawing since his diaper days but his new found love for 2D animation is what keeps him creatively busy thesedays. All of his artworks are hand-drawn on his mama's old android phone, he also likes to use his own sound effects to make his creations more livelier and dramatic.
